Description:
In the northern part of Senenthia's farmlands, you find a small group of farmers working on rebuilding a house.

When you approach, they ask if you can help them a little with the rebuilding work.

You can clearly see that they won't be able to pay you much or anything at all.
DescriptionAction: Do you want to stay and help them?
